<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Portal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        /* Basic reset and styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Navigation bar styles */
        nav {
            background-color: #333;
            padding: 1em 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin: 0;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: #575757;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* Hero section */
        .hero {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* Features section */
        .features {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        /* Footer styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation bar -->
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/home"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/jobs"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Jobs</a></li>
            <li><a href="/post-jobs"><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i> Post Jobs</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about-us"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> About Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact-us"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Contact Us</a></li>
            <li style="margin-left:auto"><a href="/logout"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero section -->
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h1>
        <p>Find the best part-time job opportunities and connect with top employers in your field. Your career starts here!</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content section -->
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Why Choose Our Job Portal?</h2>
        <div class="features">
            <!-- Feature 1 -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                <h3>Search for Jobs</h3>
                <p>Explore a wide range of job categories that fit your skills and interests. Our advanced search filters make it easy to find the perfect job for you.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Feature 2 -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-upload"></i>
                <h3>Post Job Listings</h3>
                <p>Are you an employer? Post job listings easily and find the right talent for your company. Reach thousands of potential candidates.</p>
            </div>
            <!-- Feature 3 -->
            <div class="feature-card">
                <i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i>
                <h3>Connect with Employers</h3>
                <p>Directly connect with potential employers through our platform. Build your network and get insights from industry experts.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2>About Our Job Portal</h2>
        <p>This job portal is designed to help job seekers and employers connect effortlessly. Whether you are starting your career or looking to hire, our platform provides tools and resources to make the job search and recruitment process easy and effective.</p>

        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions, suggestions, or need support, visit our <a href="/contact-us">Contact Us</a> page. We are here to assist you!</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Job Portal. All Rights Reserved. | <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> | <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
